# Node ID 48c3e964ca6b4eab71e80c48c33c1582834523d9
# Parent  ae117aa59cbe3bc960219a1e9006560cd02004b0
Bug 1544322 - Part 3 - Remove the [type] attribute for multiline <script> tags loading files in chrome://mochikit/content/

This is an autogenerated commit to handle scripts loading mochitest harness files, in
the case where the script src is on the line below the script tag.

This was generated with https://bug1544322.bmoattachments.org/attachment.cgi?id=9058170
using the `--part 3` argument.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27458

